# Practise to deploy windows web server in your own lab using the below steps

Create azure virtual machine resource with Windows Image
Connect windows VM using RDP with the credentials provided while creating VM
Install Web server (IIS) on the windows machine via Server manager
Disable the web security feature if you are practising in your own lab
Add Port 80 in NSG to allow HTTP traffic in azure portal for this VM
Check http://localhost on web server
Connect to web server using public IP address from your local computer
